</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_3-rem适配" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-rem适配" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 3.rem适配</h3>
