    <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>
<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_3-方法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-方法" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 3.方法</h3>
<p>滚动到指定页面</p>
<div class="language-javascript line-numbers-mode" data-ext="js"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code>swiper<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">slideTo</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">1000</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">false</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_4-其他参数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-其他参数" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4.其他参数</h3>
