</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="_5-监听函数" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_5-监听函数" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 5.监听函数</h3>
