    <span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="四、其他js相关" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#四、其他js相关" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 四、其他js相关</h2>
